examples.korean: Suddenly she glimpsed the truth about her sister. 발음듣기 불현듯 그녀는 언니[여동생]에 대한 진실을 깨달았다. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
examples.english: Suddenly she glimpsed the truth about her sister. 발음

examples.korean: He repudiated his first wife and married her sister. 발음듣기 그는 첫 아내와 이혼하고 그녀의 언니[여동생]와 결혼했다. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
examples.english: He repudiated his first wife and married her sister. 발음

examples.korean: She relinquished possession of the house to her sister. 발음듣기 그녀는 그 주택에 대한 소유권을 언니[여동생]에게 내주었다. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
examples.english: She relinquished possession of the house to her sister. 발음

examples.korean: She was furious at being upstaged by her younger sister. 발음듣기 그녀는 여동생에게 가려져 관심을 못 받는 것에 몹시 화가 났다. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
examples.english: She was furious at being upstaged by her younger sister. 발음

examples.korean: He gave it to his sister. 발음듣기 그는 그것을 여동생[누나]에게 주었다. Oxford Advanced Learner's English-Korean Dictionary
examples.english: He gave it to his sister. 발음
